		                        		<h1 class="newsTitle col-xs-7 col-md-8"><a href="http://www.uwpeterborough.ca/2016/02/26/point-in-time-pit-count/">Point in Time Homeless Count</a></h1>
		                        		<a href="http://www.uwpeterborough.ca/category/news" class="catLink cat_news col-xs-4 col-md-3">News</a>
		                        	</header>
		                            <div class="articleBody">
		                            				                            				                            	<div class="imgWrap">
			                            		<img class="attachment-full wp-post-image" src="http://www.uwpeterborough.ca/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/iCountPtbo.png" />
			                            	</div>
			                            			                            	
		                            	<p>
		                            		<p>Peterborough’s first Point-in-Time (PiT) Count is part of an initiative launched by the Government of Canada’s Homelessness Partnership Strategy (HPS). Communities across Canada will participate in a coordinated PiT Count to build a national picture of homelessness by counting the number of people experiencing absolute homelessness and surveying them to understand their demographics and service&#8230;</p>
		                            				                            		<a class="read-more" href="http://www.uwpeterborough.ca/2016/02/26/point-in-time-pit-count/">Read More</a>	
		                            	</p>
